OL,3,CITV 70 coverage oversimplifying the
OL,4,Cchannel's past
OL,6,GSometimes the story of the present is
OL,7,Glost in the misrepresentation or
OL,8,Gmisunderstanding of the past.
OL,10,FThis is the case with some of the
OL,11,Fcoverage of ITV's 70th anniversary.
OL,13,FIt is too easy to distort the
OL,14,Fchannel's story by oversimplification
OL,15,Fand present the past 70 years as one
OL,16,Fsimple journey.
OL,18,FThis matters.
OL,20,FHistory in all its forms can simply
OL,21,Fbecome the story of the victorious.
