OL,3,CITV 70 coverage oversimplifying the
OL,4,Cchannel's past
OL,6,FIt was the most serious-minded of the
OL,7,Fmajor network companies. Nearly all
OL,8,Fits significant programmes were rooted
OL,9,Fin the north of England culturally or
OL,10,Fsocially. It made many fine programmes
OL,11,F` serious dramas and documentaries `
OL,12,Fwhich were not obviously "commercial".
OL,14,FBut Granada was the fourth ITV company
OL,15,Fto go on the air ` behind Associated
OL,16,FRediffusion, ATV and ABC.
OL,18,FTo suggest the regional companies were
OL,19,Fmere "news hubs" is simply
OL,20,Fdisrespectful.
