OL,6,FDo we really believe that people over
OL,7,Fthe age of 40 do not know what
OL,8,FIndependent Television was?
OL,10,FI thought I'd try to condense the
OL,11,Fhistory of the network accurately into
OL,12,Fa few short paragraphs. Surely this
OL,13,Fwould be more fitting than sone of the
OL,14,Fblurb in recent days?
OL,16,FCommercial television in Britain is 70
OL,17,Fyears old.
