OL,3,CITV 70 coverage oversimplifying the
OL,4,Cchannel's past
OL,6,FThe first two commercial broadcasters
OL,7,Fin the UK ` Associated Rediffusion and
OL,8,FATV ` started broadcasting in the
OL,9,FLondon area in September 1955. Neither
OL,10,Fare still in business.
OL,12,FOver the next seven years, other
OL,13,Fcompanies began broadcasting across
OL,14,Fmost of the rest of the country.
OL,16,FThese companies were all fiercely
OL,17,Findependent of each other ` serving
OL,18,Ftheir local areas while also acting
OL,19,Ftogether as a network.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/8
