OL,6,FThe regional map was redrawn
OL,7,Fsignificantly in 1968 and further
OL,8,Fmodified as a result of the switch to
OL,9,FUHF transmission.
OL,11,FBut, more significantly, many
OL,12,Fcompanies changed over the years
OL,13,Fthrough franchise rounds run by the
OL,14,Fregulator.
OL,16,FAfter 1993, the regional companies
OL,17,Fstarted to merge with each other.
OL,18,FEventually one company owned all the
OL,19,Flicences outside Scotland.
