OL,3,CITV 70 coverage oversimplifying the
OL,4,Cchannel's past
OL,6,FToday ITV plc runs a national channel
OL,7,Fcalled ITV 1. But the service includes
OL,8,Fregional news and advertising plus
OL,9,Fsome bespoke programmes for Wales and
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,FSome regional companies came and went
OL,13,Fin the franchise rounds ` some
OL,14,Fsurvived and have their legacy within
OL,15,FITV plc.
OL,17,FOf course, this is a huge
OL,18,Fsimplification but surely it is at
OL,19,Fleast an accurate summary?
OL,21,FThe past is another country. ITV's
OL,22,Fanniversary is a cause for celebration.
